<template>
    <EmulationTitleHeader></EmulationTitleHeader>
    <EmulationTitleTable></EmulationTitleTable>
    <EmulationTitleFooter></EmulationTitleFooter>
    <EmulationTitleForm></EmulationTitleForm>
</template>

<script>
import EmulationTitleForm from './EmulationTitleForm.vue';
import EmulationTitleTable from './EmulationTitleTable.vue';
import EmulationTitleHeader from './EmulationTitleHeader.vue';
import EmulationTitleFooter from './EmulationTitleFooter.vue';
export default {
    name: "EmulationTitleHome",
    components: {
        EmulationTitleForm, EmulationTitleTable, EmulationTitleHeader, EmulationTitleFooter
    },
    mounted() {
        const plugin = document.createElement("script");
        plugin.setAttribute(
            "src",
            "http://localhost:8080/assets/font/fontawesome-pro-6.1.1-web/all.min.js"
        );
        plugin.async = true;
        document.body.appendChild(plugin);
    },
}
</script>

<style></style>
